data.description: Largest Corner Lot in the neighborhood! This charming single-family house offers 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms, a bonus family room, an enclosed Florida room, and an enclosed front porch with beautiful arches. The layout provides an abundance of space, making it the largest ideal for entertaining friends and family. Key highlights include a 2-car garage, a NEW 2019 fenced backyard for privacy, a NEW 2020 POOL, and an open-concept chef's dream kitchen with ample storage! NEW Upgrades: 2019 AC, 2019 Roof, and 2019 Impact windows/doors. Family-friendly neighborhood near University Drive and Taft Street, close to top-rated schools, restaurants, and shops. Schedule a viewing and call today! Please do not disturb the Owners - Do not show up without an appointment!
